Citation.sTitle: Volumetric and Viscometric Behavior of the Binary System: (Hexan-1-ol + p-Xylene)
Citation.sAbstract: Densities and viscosities for the binary mixtures of hexan-1-ol with p-xylene have been measured at a number of mole fractions at T = (303.15, 313.15, and 323.15) K. The excess molar volumes and viscosity deviations have been calculated from the experimental results and have been fitted to the Redlich-Kister polynomial equation.
sAuthor: Rahman, I. M. M.[Ismail M. M.]
